name: STrAn93
description: You've awakened in a strange place, you will meet strange allies and foes. The one thing that will set all that apart is trust. There are 6 possible Endings, "The bad", "The worst", "The truth", "The good", "The saved", and "The aight ima head out". Some are hidden so pay attention as to how to get to them. Search every nook and cranny, Have a chat with the enemies or allies. There is always something unexpected in the Witch's Manor. Hope you enjoy !
